description.fr: Détruire tous les {ObjectMechanism:716, plural:other}. \--- Lorsqu'un {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} subit une ATTAQUE\_: Les {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME, plural:other} autour\_ de l'attaquant s'ENVOLENT. \--- Lorsqu'un {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} meurt\_: Invoque un {Summoning:921} autour\_ d'un {ObjectMechanism:716!}.
description.en: Destroy all the {ObjectMechanism:716, plural:other}. \--- When a {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} endures an ATTACK: The {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME, plural:other} around\_ the attacker TAKE FLIGHT. \--- When a {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} dies: Summons one {Summoning:921} around\_ a {ObjectMechanism:716!}.
description.es: Destruir todos los {ObjectMechanism:716, plural:other}. \--- Cuando un {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} sufre un ATAQUE: Los {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME, plural:other} alrededor\_ del atacante ALCEN EL VUELO. \--- Cuando un {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} muere: Invoca un {Summoning:921} alrededor\_ de un {ObjectMechanism:716!}.
description.de: Zerstöre alle {ObjectMechanism:716, plural:other}. \--- Wenn ein {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} einen ANGRIFF erleidet: Die {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME, plural:other} im Umkreis vom\_ Angreifer HEBEN AB. \--- Wenn ein {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} stirbt: Beschwört einen {Summoning:921} im Umkreis von\_ einem {ObjectMechanism:716!}.
description.pt: Destruir todos os {ObjectMechanism:716, plural:other}. \--- Quando um {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} sofre um ATAQUE: Os {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME, plural:other} em\_volta\_ do atacante DECOLAM. \--- Quando um {%FAMILY_TOFU_NAME} morre: Invoca um {Summoning:921} em\_volta\_ de um {ObjectMechanism:716!}.
